commit.message: Simplify support for major Qt versions.

fix: check for valid context #61

According to Qt6 documentation widget->context() can return a nullptr for the QOpenGLContext in case the widget has not been exposed. This is the case when loaded into Qt Designer.
fix: Update ChangeLog creation command for git.
Use latest download packages in CI. [skip ci]
Fix changed Qt package name in Appveyor CI.
Update build matrix in AppVeyor script. [skip ci]
